[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    738[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     of mmHg. The catalog drives the canonical unit; this helper
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    739[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     handles the small number of conversions the demo needs.
