[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1559[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1560[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # Step 1: validate and normalize.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1561[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     cleaned = ingest_and_normalize(
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1562[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         record, s3, dead_letter_bucket)
