[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1599[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     surface, reasons = evaluate_alert(state, decision, now_dt)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1600[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     if not surface:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1601[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         log_suppressed_alert(
