[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1603[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             suppressed_bucket, run_id, now_dt)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1604[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         cloudwatch.put_metric_data(
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1605[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             Namespace=CLOUDWATCH_NAMESPACE,
