[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1640[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             device_quality_bucket, dead_letter_bucket, run_id)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1641[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         counts[outcome] += 1
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1642[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
