[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1645[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                     "suppressed", "surfaced"):
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1646[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         print(f"  {outcome:>10}: {counts[outcome]}")
