[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1649[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1650[0m:[38;5;10m[49m def run_demo():
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1651[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """Run the pipeline end-to-end against the in-memory mocks.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1652[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1653[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     No AWS resources are touched; every external dependency is
